With the increasing number of Android versions and devices from different manufacturers, it is likely that this app may not work perfectly on all models. 

Especially the video settings are device-dependent, but you can see which combinations have worked for other users: 

 http://dailyroads.com/voyager/stats.php 

Currently known issues are listed on this page: 

 http://dailyroads.com/voyager/m/issues 

If the problem you experience is not listed on the page above, please write us a detailed description on the issue using this comment form: 

 http://dailyroads.com/voyager/m/comments 

We welcome any feedback, but praises and 5* ratings are best directed to the Market from where you downloaded the app. 

If you have recently upgraded to the latest version, and it causes problems on your device, please try to uninstall and reinstall. You can also download and install the earlier version of the app from the link below: 

 http://dailyroads.com/voyager/m/download
